{
  "id": "adv_main_02_05_03",
  "title": "東京編1章23話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ。私の英語全然通じなくて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s so true‚ though! Nobody understood my English.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのフィーリングだよ～\n芽衣なんて猫ちゃんとだってお話出来ちゃうよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all about feelings‚ though.\nI can communicate with kitties‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.200000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカでLizNoirが成功したのは\n私がセンターとして大活躍したおかげなんですよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason why LizNoir was a success in the US\nwas because I gave epic performances as the center!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.566666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカで一番人気だったのは神崎さん……\nウソは、いけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The most popular member in the US was Kanzaki-san.\nLying is wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.907302284240725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ！　サニピと月ストのメンバーがリズノワと\n仲睦まじく……！　尊過ぎます！　奇跡発見！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhh! Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest members getting cozy with LizNoir!\nIt’s just too precious! A miraculous find!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.307302284240723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこれではちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nshouldn’t we be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1739689509074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 38.00730228424073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……\nとても事件の話なんて出来る状態じゃないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well…\nThis isn’t the best atmosphere to discuss a scandal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.57396895090739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。おーいみんな、悪いけど今日の所は\n部屋に戻って親睦会をやってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good point. Hey‚ girls! Sorry‚ but could you\ntake the party into your rooms?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.04063561757406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.773968950907395,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 666.6666666666572,
          "startTime": 51.44063561757405
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666666666629,
          "startTime": 51.84063561757406
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "神崎さんと天動さんは残ってくれるかな？\n今後のことを今から話したい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kanzaki-san‚ Tendo-san‚ can you both stay behind?\nI want to discuss the plan moving forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.00730228424072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、もちろんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.34063561757406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。あっ、優とすみれは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. Oh! What about Yu and Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.27396895090739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はリーダーの君達だけにしよう。もしかしたら\n他の子に聞かせたくない話になるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s make it just the leaders today. Just a hunch‚\nbut we might bring up things the others shouldn’t hear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.94063561757406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか、分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.00730228424072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 73.5739689509074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirまで解雇……？　そんな……\nあの人は、会社をどうするつもりなの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He fired LizNoir‚ too? No way…\nWhat is he doing with that company?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.40730228424071,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8933.333333333338,
          "startTime": 87.34063561757405
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "今回の事件でバンプロのイメージも地に落ちたわ\nネットでも、随分叩かれているし。見て、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This scandal has really tarnished Van Productions’ reputation.\nThey’re even canceling him on the internet. Just look at this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7073022842407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルを金儲けの道具にした……ファンの気持ちを）\n（裏切った金の亡者……痛烈に批判されてるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（He used his idols as pawns for profit… He betrayed the fans…）\n（He’s money-hungry… That’s some intense hate he’s getting.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.87396895090734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "何が書いてあるんですか？\n私にも見せて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are they saying about him?\nLet me see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.240635617574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、君は見ない方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you shouldn’t see it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2339689754304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "見せてあげましょう\nどうせ、彼女も自分で調べてしまうわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let her see it.\nShe’ll just look it up on her own later anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.13396897543043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、隠しても無駄よ\n私も瑠依も、現実から目を逸らしては前に進めないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ there’s no point in hiding it.\nRui and I both can’t move on unless we see the truth with our own eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.33396897543044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 118.53396897543044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nファンの人達の気持ちも分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………\nI understand where the fans are coming from.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "冷徹な人ではありました\nでも、あの人は決してアイドルを単なる道具とは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He could be cold-hearted.\nBut he never saw us idols merely as pawns…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.16730230876372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……今にして思えば、三枝さんがいなくなった後\nLizNoirが存続出来たのは朝倉さんがいたからよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking back now‚ after Saegusa-san disappeared‚\nLizNoir only survived because we had Asakura-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5673023087639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "活動休止後も、朝倉さんは私をLizNoirに\n戻してくれた。そのことは、今でも感謝してるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after my hiatus‚ Asakura-san let me rejoin LizNoir.\nI’m still grateful for that‚ even now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.03396897543072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんのいないLizNoirなんて、ありえない\nあの人は、それが分かっていたんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t imagine LizNoir without you‚ Rio-san.\nAnd I think he understood that‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.20063564209732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんは代わりのメンバーを探してたみたいだけど\n葵さん同様、首を縦に振らなかったみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ Himeno-san looked for replacements‚\nbut Aoi-san never approved any of them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.30063564209732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "新メンバーの加入や海外留学も\n結果的にはLizNoirをさらに飛躍させたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The new members and the training abroad\nultimately did give LizNoir more exposure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.00063564209725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
